IMPORTANT SAFETY NOTICE:

This software is designed for automotive diagnostic purposes. When using features
such as ECU flashing, module encoding, or actuator tests:

1. Always ensure stable power supply to prevent damage to vehicle electronics
2. Use at your own risk - improper use may cause vehicle malfunction
3. The authors and contributors are NOT liable for any damage caused to vehicles,
   property, or persons resulting from the use of this software
4. Consult with qualified automotive professionals before performing advanced operations
5. Backup original ECU firmware before any flashing operations

